OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan ordered to compensate
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwartime 'comfort women'    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A South Korean court has ordered Japan 
OL,6, to compensate a group of women who were
OL,7, forced to work in military brothels    
OL,8, during World War Two.                  
OL,10,FThe 16 women, who were kept as sex     
OL,11,Fslaves for Japanese soldiers,          
OL,12,Fpreviously had their case dismissed.   
OL,14,FThey filed a lawsuit in 2016 but Seoul 
OL,15,FCentral District Court dismissed it    
OL,16,Ffive years later, citing sovereign     
OL,17,Fimmunity.                              
OL,19,FThe Seoul High Court have now          
OL,20,Foverturned the ruling.                 
